Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson muri Imperial College, bwagaragaje ko gukomeza kwitandukanya n'abandi bizakenerwa "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rufite ubushobozi (bishoboka ko ruzaba rumaze amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
