Taiwan yongereye ibikorwa byo gukora udupfukamunwa ndetse n'ibihano byo gutunga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.Ibishushanyo byo mu Bwongereza na Amerika bigaragaza ko kugabanya (bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo ariko ntibigikomeze) no kugabanya (bihindura ukwiyongera kw'icyorezo) bifite imbogamizi zikomeye.
Imishinga myiza yo kugabanya uburwayi ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abaganga bakeneye ubuvuzi mu bice bibiri bya gatatu n'abapfa mu gice, ariko ikanazana abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi bapfa kandi ikangiza gahunda z'ubuzima.
Gufata urukingo bishobora guhitamo, ariko rukwiye gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikwirakwira mu baturage (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba ruhari, niba ari rwo rubanza), kuko mu gihe cy'ubutabire, gukwirakwiza bikongera guhita bikorwa vuba igihe ingamba zishyushye.
Gufata ingamba mu gihe kirekire zo kurwanya icyorezo bibangamiye imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta miti yihariye ya virusi yemewe ya COVID-19, ariko hari ingufu zikomeje gukorwa kugira ngo ikorwe, harimo no gupima imiti iriho.
Gufata imiti yo kugabanya ibicurane, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora gufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bivanye n'uburemere bw'icyo kibazo, ushobora gukenera imiti ifasha mu kuvura umwuka, imiti ifasha mu kuvura mu muhogo no gufashwa guhumeka.
Gukoresha steroids bishobora gutuma ingaruka ziba mbi kurushaho.
Hari imiti myinshi y'indwara z'indwara z'umugera wa COVID-19 yari yemewe mbere y'aho ikomeje gushakishwa.
OMS yavuze kandi ko hari "imiti yo mu rugo n'imiti gakondo" ishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso byatewe na SARS-CoV-19.
OMS ivuga ko kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ubuvuzi n'ibyifuzo by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ari ingamba z'ingenzi zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC n'Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Gishinzwe Uburayi (OMS Regional Office for Europe) bashyizeho amabwiriza agenewe ibitaro n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kugira ngo bagere ku rwego rw'uburyo bwo kongera gukoresha ibikoresho, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu gukora ibizamini bya COVID-19, guhagarika imikorere y'ubushakashatsi aho bishoboka, gutandukanya no kwiherera abarwayi bafite COVID-19 no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bakomeye binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'imyanya y'ubuhumekero n'ibitanda bihari.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku kuntu icyorezo cya mbere (cyitwa umurwayi wa NULL) gishobora kuba cyaraturutse.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko afite coronavirus nshya ashobora kugaruka ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi byari bifitanye isano cyane cyane n'isoko ry'ibinyabuzima byo mu mazi rya Huanan, na ryo ryaragurishaga inyamaswa zibayeho, kandi igitekerezo ni uko virusi yavuye kuri imwe muri izo nyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ko ifite inkomoko ya zoonotic. Ku wa 26 Ukuboza, habayeho ingamba z'ubwandu bw'amaraso bw'imvumba butangwa n'impamvu itazwi z'ibyabaye Dr. Zhang Jixian ku bitaro bya Hubei Provincial Hospital, akaba yarabitangaje kuri CDC ya Jianghan mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku wa 27 Ukuboza.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan ryagabishije bagenzi babo ku "coronavirus isa na SARS".
Polisi yacyashye abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, kubera gukwirakwiza ibinyoma, naho undi muganga witwa Ai Fen, yacyashwe n'abayobozi be kubera ko yatanze iyo mburi.
Nyuma yaho, ku wa 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan yasohoye itangazo rusange maze irimenyesha OMS.
Mu ntangiriro za Mutarama, abantu benshi bari bamaze kumenyekana ko bafite ubumuga bw'amaraso bufite impamvu zitazwi, ku buryo abategetsi b'ubuzima bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan batangiye iperereza.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'u Bushinwa, bigaterwa n'impunzi zo mu Bushinwa z'umwaka mushya ndetse n'uko Wuhan ari ihuriro ry'ingendo n'umuhanda w'umurenge w'umurenge w'umurenge.
