Mu byo abaturage b'igihugu bakoze harimo gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba zo kwirinda, urugero nko gushyiramo abantu mu kato (zwi nka "guhagarara mu rugo", "gucika imyanya y'ubuhungiro" cyangwa "gufungwa") no guhagarika imirimo y'akazi. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bakorera mu buryo runaka bwo gufungwa muri Amerika, abantu barenga miriyoni 50 bari mu kato muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 59 bari muri Afurika y'Epfo, naho abantu miriyoni 1300 bari mu kato mu Buhinde.
