Ku wa 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatanze itangazo ryo kwanga guhura n'abantu no gukora ingendo zose zitari ngombwa, agasaba abantu gukora bava mu ngo zabo igihe cyose bishoboka, bakirinda ahantu nk'amabara, amafunguro n'ibibuga by'imikino.
