Mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko byari bimeze mu ngingo zabanjirije iyi, polisi yashoboraga gusaba ko ibyo bihano byakurikizwa binyuze mu gutanga amande no gusenya amateraniro.
Byinshi mu bigo byategetswe gufunga, uretse ibyo byiswe 'ibikenewe' harimo ibigo by'ubucuruzi, ibigo by'ubuvuzi, amabanki, ibigo by'ubucuruzi, ibigo by'amavuta n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Tariki ya 20 Mutarama, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cya mbere kizwi cyagaragaye muri leta ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika, mu mugabo wari wasubiye mu gihugu cye avuye i Wuhan ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama.
Tariki ya 29 Mutarama, hashyizweho itsinda ry'akazi ku coronavirus ry'Izu ry'Abirabura.
