Amashuri yo mu gace ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku wa 3 Werurwe, mu gihe mu giharage cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yafunzwe. Ku wa 6 Werurwe 2020, itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara zo mu rwego rw'indwara zo mu rwego rw'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa Coronavirus bo muri Imperial College London batangaje ku gihugu cya Amerika ibipimo by'ingaruka za coronavirus nshya.
Kuri uyu munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ry'imigabane y'inyongera yo kwitegura no guhangana na Coronavirus, ryashyize inkunga ya miliyari 8300 z'amadolari mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi ku nzego za leta kugira ngo zitabire iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho amategeko agenga ingendo ku bakozi, asesa inama kandi atera abakozi inkunga yo gukora imirimo yo mu rugo.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko ibihugu byinshi byo mu Burayi, uretse u Bwongereza, bizabura ingendo mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yongeyeho ko ibyo bihano byari byarabuzanyijwe, bigatuma n'u Bwongereza na Irilande biboneka.
