Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi byo muri Amerika byafunze cyangwa bigabanya amasaha byakoraga kugira ngo bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu majyaruguru 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko umujyi wa New York wari ufite abantu 10 700 banduye coronavirus, birenze umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku itariki ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko ububangukirane mu by'imibereho y'abaturage busa n'aho bukora, kuko ibipimo by'abantu baguye mu mirimo y'ubwiyongere byavuye ku minsi 2 bikagera ku minsi 4.7.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32 308 banduye muri New York City, abantu 672 bakaba barapfuye bazize virusi. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Amerika ifite ubwandu bwa coronavirus bwuzuye kurusha ikindi gihugu cyose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, hari abantu 400 335 banduye muri Amerika bapfuye 12.841.
Amakuru atangwa n'itangazamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, avuga ko Perezida Trump wa Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, yafashe ubwato bwa USNS Comfort, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1000, buhagarara i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, Amerika yari ifite imibare y'abantu 884 bapfuye mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 kubera coronavirus.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, muri Leta ya New York, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100.000.Inzu Yera yahawe ibisobanuro byo gupfobya iterabwoba no kugenzura ubutumwa, mu guhamagara abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga bagategura itangazo rusange n'ibitabo bifitanye isano na virusi hamwe n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Kuba Trump yarakomeje guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ingorane mu buryo butunguranye, byashyizwe mu rujijo hagati y'abashyigikiye ishyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abanyamakuru banenze uburyo Amerika ishingiye ku kwinjiza ibikoresho by'ingenzi, harimo ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byihariye, mu Bushinwa.
Ubushakashatsi ku ngengabitekerezo z'ingendo bwakoreshejwe mu kumenya no guhanura ingengabitekerezo z'ubwirakabiri, bwasohotse mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020.
Hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu 2018 y'Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Ubwogero bw'Indege, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei bafite umubare munini w'abagenzi baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari ahantu hazwi cyane ku bantu bavaga i Wuhan.
Byatangajwe ko Bali ariwo mujyi udashoboye cyane mu mijyi 20 ikundwa cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi ya Australia yo ibonwa ko ifite ubushobozi bwinshi.Ku wa 7 Gashyantare, Australia yashyize ahagaragara gahunda yayo yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Yatangaje ko hakiri byinshi byo kuvumbura kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu gusubiza icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, Australia yatangaje ko hari imimerere y'ubutabire bw'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko imodoka z'abaturage zihagaritswe neza mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu bitandukanye byateganyaga guhunga abaturage n'abakozi ba bya dipolomasi bo muri ako gace, cyane cyane ku ndege z'indege z'igihugu by'iwabo, byemejwe n'ubuyobozi bw'u Bushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Arjantine, Ubudage na Tayilande ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byateguye guhunga abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazatura umuturage n'umwe wo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Brazil yavanye muri icyo gihugu abantu 34 bo muri icyo gihugu cyangwa bene wabo, usibye Abanyapolonye bane, Umushinwa n'Umunya Buhinde.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde baramanutse muri Polonye, aho indege ya Brazil yafashe ikirindiro mbere yo gukomeza urugendo rwayo yerekeza muri Brazil.
Abaturage ba Brazil bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bo mu ndege ya mbere na 39 bo mu ndege ya kabiri ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bajya muri CFB Trenton kugira ngo bagume mu kato mu byumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indege yindi yageze muri CFB Trenton irimo Abakanada 185 bari i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi ba Australia bahungiye mu kigo cy'ibohero cya Christmas Island, cyari cyongeye gushyirwa mu kato, aho bagumye iminsi 14.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, indege yo kuvanaho abantu yavuye muri Nouvelle-Zélande igeze i Auckland; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya no muri Pasifika) bagumye mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zari gusura Abanyamerika bari ku bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 bari bavuye mu ndege ya Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, muri Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, Guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye guhunga abaturage bayo ba Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari yaraguzwe na Guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yasubije mu gihugu abaturage 112 ba Afurika y'Epfo.
Hakozwe ibizamini by'ubuvuzi mbere yo gutwara indege, kandi Abanyafurika y'Epfo bane bari bafite ibimenyetso bya coronavirus bagombaga kugumaho kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Gusa Abanyarwanda b'Abanyafurika y'Epfo basuzumye nabi, nibo bonyine basubijwe mu gihugu.
Ibisubizo by'igeragezwa byemereye Abanyafurika y'Epfo bose, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abapayilote, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bagize uruhare mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bagumye mu isuzuma no mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri The Ranch Resort.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Irak mu buryo bufatiweho kubera icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (birimo u Bubiligi, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje ubufasha mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri Kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha kohereza ubufasha mu turere two mu Bushinwa twazahajwe na virusi, kandi bivugwa ko itsinda rihuriye mu gace ka Chicago, ryashoboye kohereza udupfukamunwa 50 000 twa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje inkunga ya miriyoni 100 z'amadolari ku kigo cy'umuryango w'abibumbye cyita ku buzima (OMS) yo gushyigikira ibikorwa byo gushaka urukingo no kuvurwa, ndetse no kurinda "abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no mu majyepfo ya Aziya".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko Leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 kuri Filipine ku wa 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapour yatangaje ko izohereza inkunga y'amadolari miliyoni 2.26 mu Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze agapfukamunwa ka miliyoni imwe i Wuhan, Turukiya yoherereza ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwoherereza toni zisaga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Malaysia itangaza ko yoherereje u Bushinwa imyenda y'ubuvuzi ya miliyoni 18, Ubudage bwoherereza ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitandukanye birimo imyenda 10.000 ikoreshwa mu gukora ibintu by'ubumara, Amerika yoherereza Ubushinwa toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, kandi isezeranya ko izajya iha inkunga y'ubukungu y'ibindi miriyoni 100 z'amadolari ku bihugu byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umushoramari Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho by'igeragezwa miliyoni 1.1 n'imishishi miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60 000 yo kurinda abantu i Addis Abeba muri Etiyopiya, kugira ngo ishyirahamwe ry'ubumwe bwa Afurika ribitanga.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho 5000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'imashini 5 zo guhumeka muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada.A Buholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech bavuze ko bafite impungenge ku maskara n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakorewe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye ibikoresho 58 000 by'igeragezwa rya coronavirus byakorewe mu Bushinwa ku gipimo cyo kwibonera neza ku kigero cya 30% gusa, mu gihe u Buholandi bwavuyemo udupfukamunwa 600.000 tw'Abashinwa tutagikora neza.
U Bubiligi bwafashe udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudakoreshwa, twibwiraga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'Ubushinwa bwaremewe cyane mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika.Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangiye ibikorwa by'ubufasha b'ubutabazi ku bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimiye imbaraga z'ubuyobozi bw'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya no gukumira iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, igihe abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga ibanga ryabangamiye imihati yo kwirinda no gukumira, n'ikibazo kiriho ubu, aho Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa "yahaye amakuru y'igihe cyose kugira ngo yirinde guterwa ubwoba n'iminsi mikuru y'Umwaka Mushya w'ukwezi".
Ku wa 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo gushyiraho itegeko ribuza gutwara abantu mu mujyi wa Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya ko atari inama OMS yatanze", "ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cy'umwiyemezo wo gukumira icyorezo aho kigaragarira cyane" kandi ko "nta karengane kabonetse mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku wa 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko abantu batwara indwara hagati y'abantu hanze y'Ubushinwa n'umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyihutirwa cy'ubuzima rusange gifite akamaro mpuzamahanga (ESPII), ari icya gatandatu ESPII kuva icyo cyorezo cyatangiriye gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu mwaka wa 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko ESPII yari "ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make kandi bitagira gahunda zikomeye z'ubuzima".
Mu gusubiza ku ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'ingamba z'ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zitangiza ubudasa mu bucuruzi n'ingendo mpuzamahanga" kandi ko "OMS idasaba kugabanya ubucuruzi cyangwa ingendo".
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango w'isi yose inkunga ya miriyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira imyiteguro y'ingamba mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushyigikira ibihugu "bitagira uburyo bwo gutahura abantu banduye iyo virusi, mu gihe byaba bibaye".
Tedros kandi yagize icyo avuga avuga ko "turi intwari gusa nk'uruzitiro rwacu rworoheje" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "guhora ushyiraho amafaranga cyangwa ukishyura menshi mu gihe kiri imbere".
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko umunyamabanga mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, António Guterres, yari yemeye gutanga "imbaraga z'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryose mu gusubiza".
Ibi byatumye itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'amafaranga rigira uruhare mu kurwanya iyi ndwara, rifasha ibihugu byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye guhuza uburyo bwo kuyikemura, WHO ivuga ko bizatuma "bibanda ku bibazo by'ubuzima mu gihe ibindi bigo bishobora gutanga ubumenyi bwabyo bwihariye mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'iki cyorezo mu by'imibereho myiza, ubukungu n'iterambere".
Ku wa 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'umurimo ufatanyije uyobowe na OMS n'Ubushinwa ryashyizwe mu bikorwa kugira ngo rihe impuguke mpuzamahanga n'iz'umuryango w'abibumbye ku butaka mu Bushinwa kugira ngo zifashe mu miyoborere y'igihugu no gupima "uburemere n'ubwirakwiriye bw'iki cyorezo" binyuze mu gutegura imyigaragambyo n'inama n'ibigo bikomeye ku rwego rw'igihugu no gusura aho hantu kugira ngo hagendewe ku "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'intara, harimo imiterere y'imijyi n'icyaro". Ku wa 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi kurushaho kugira ngo yitegure icyorezo cya Coronavirus gishobora kuba", ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane ko icyorezo kiza, ibihugu bigomba kuba "mu cyiciro cyo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo kiri gutera imbere muri Irani, OMS yoherejeyo itsinda ry'umurimo ufatanyije kugira ngo rigenzure imimerere. Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko igenzura ry'iterabwoba rya coronavirus ku isi yose rizamuka kuva "ryisumbuye" kugeza "ryisumbuye cyane", rikaba ari ryo rwego rwo hejuru rwo kuburira no gupima ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi ushinzwe gahunda y'ubutabazi bw'ubuzima muri OMS, yatanze umuburo mu itangazo ati "Iki ni ikimenyamenya cy'uko ubutegetsi bwose bw'isi bufite ukuri: nimukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi tugomba kuba twiteguye", ashimangira ko ingamba zo gusubiza neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane".
Ryan yavuze kandi ko amakuru y'ubu atagaragariza ko abayobozi b'ubuzima bwa rusange batangaza icyorezo ku isi hose, kandi avuga ko icyo gitangazo cyasobanuraga ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko abantu bose ku isi bazaba baranduye iyo virusi".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo cy'icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru yavuze ko OMS yari "ihangayikishijwe cyane, haba ku rugero ruteye ubwoba rwo gukwirakwira no gukomera, ndetse no ku rugero ruteye ubwoba rwo kudakora". OMS yahawe ibisobanuro bikomeye ku byo ifata nk'uburyo butari bwiza bwo gucunga icyorezo, harimo gutangaza mu gihe cyashize ko ari icyihutirwa cy'ubuzima rusange ndetse no gushyira virusi mu cyiciro cy'icyorezo.
Igisubizo cy'abatabyemera cy'ibyifuzo by'umukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye w'abibumbye Tedros Adhanom, cyasinywe n'abantu 733 000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere z'umuryango w'abibumbye ku burenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu zemeza ko uburenganzira bw'abantu bose bubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Iri tsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira ibyo akora bizakiza ubuzima kandi ko Guverinoma ifite inshingano.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura uburyo cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bidakwiye kwigera bikoreshwa nk'impamvu yo guhaririza itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko abantu bose bafite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abafite ubumuga, abafite ubumuga, abageze mu za bukuru, abahunze mu gihugu, abafite ubutaka, abafite ubukene bukabije, abafunzwe, impunzi n'abandi bantu bataramenyekana bakeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ya leta irimo guhangana n'ingaruka z'ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage byatewe na COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Iterambere ry'Igihugu watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru yuzuye kandi y'igihe ku bibazo by'ingamba za politiki mu bihugu byo ku isi, ndetse n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku migambi yo gukomeza imibereho myiza y'isi n'ubukungu kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka zo gufunga no gufunga ingendo, iki kigo cya digitale kirimo ikurikirana politiki ku gihugu, kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku bandi no korohereza igisubizo cy'isi yose gihuza n'ikibazo cya coronavirus.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Minisitiri w'Ibiro bya Kabine y'Ubwongereza, Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, kubera uburyo yakemuye iki cyorezo, cyatangiye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi batandukanye b'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti bo mu Bushinwa (PCC) ku rwego rw'intara barakuwe kubera uko bakoreshaga imbaraga z'ikigeragezo cyo gushyira mu kato abantu mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, mu kugaragaza ko batishimiye uko gahunda ya politiki yitabiriye iki cyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko iki gikorwa cyafashwe kugira ngo umwanditsi mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, Xi Jinping, arinde umujinya w'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'u Bushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyatangiye i Wuhan, mu cyerekezo cy'ibitekerezo by'amayeri ku nkomoko ya COVID-19 muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika bwavuze ko Coronavirus ari "virusi y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan", kandi ko "ubushinjacyaha bw'Ubushinwa bwatanze ibiribwa birenze kuri virusi ubu imaze guhinduka icyorezo cy'icyorezo ku isi", ibyo bikaba byaravuzwe n'abacamanza bamwe na bamwe ko ari urwikekwe n' "uburiganya ku kuba ubutegetsi bwayo bwarananiwe gukumira iki cyorezo".
The Daily Beast yabonye telegram ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ivuga ko hari uburyo bwo gutumanaho bwari buturutse mu Nama y'Umutekano w'Igihugu, kandi ko ubwo buryo bwari bwaravuzwe ngo "All About China".
Twagiye tubwirwa ko tugomba kugerageza gutangaza ubwo butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama z'abanyamakuru n'ibiganiro kuri televiziyo. "Ibitangazamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imihati y'Ubushinwa yo kohereza ubufasha mu bihugu byugarijwe na virusi ari igice cy'imyivumbagatanyo yo gushaka kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Umuhagarariye politiki y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi, Josep Borrell, yatanze umuburo ko "hariho igice cya politiki y'isi kirimo kurwanya ingufu binyuze mu kwamamaza no muri politiki y'ubuntu".
Borrell yavuze kandi ko "Ubushinwa burimo butanga ubutumwa ko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufana ushoboye kandi wiringirwa".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye ko Amerika yakuyeho ibihano byafatiwe Syria, Venezuela na Iran, mu gihe bivugwa ko yohereje ubufasha muri ibyo bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, ibihano bya Amerika byabujije Jack Ma gutanga udupfukamunwa 100,000 kuri Cuba.
Nanone bashinjwa ko abayobozi ba Amerika bayobora imfashanyo zigenewe ibindi bihugu mu gihugu cyabo.
