Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rivuga ko abarwayi binjira bagomba gutandukana mu byumba bitandukanye by'abategereje bitewe n'uko bakekwaho cyangwa badafite COVID-19. Uretse izindi bwoko bw'imashini zo kurinda umuntu, OSHA ivuga ko abantu bakora ku birenge by'ibirenge 6 ku barwayi banduye cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura SARS-CoV-2 n'abakora ingendo zo gukora aerosols.
