OMS itera inkunga gusa ko abakozi bashyiraho amabwiriza y'abarwayi bakoresha agapfukamunwa mu gihe baba bagiye gukora ubuvuzi.
Ku bantu bafatira ibipimo by'ubuhumekero by'abarwayi ba COVID-19, bakabitaho cyangwa bakabijyana batabanje gukora ingamba zo gukora aerosols, OMS itera inkunga ko bakoresha agapfukamunwa, insozi cyangwa igakingira mu maso, ikanzu n'amagufwa.
