Kubera ko gutanga ibikoresho byo kurinda umuntu ku giti cye bidahagije, OMS igasaba kugabanya cyane ko hakenewe kubikoresha, ugasimbuza ubuvuzi bwa telefoni, inzitizi z'umubiri nko ku madirishya asobanutse, kugabanya uruhushya rwo kwinjira mu cyumba cy'umurwayi wa COVID-19 ku bantu gusa bari mu kwitabwaho kwe ku giti cye, gukoresha agapfukamunwa kamwe kitakuweho mu gihe hakorwa kwita ku barwayi benshi bafite indwara imwe, kugenzura no guhuza umurongo w'ibikoresho byo kurinda umuntu ku giti cye no guhungabanya gukoresha agapfukamunwa n'abantu badafite ibimenyetso.
