Icy'ingenzi cy'umurimo wa ECA2 ni ugukurikirana ECA.
ECA isohora homoni ya angiotensin I igakora angiotensin II, ari yo ikora ubwonko.
ECA2 nayo ikuraho amino acid carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine iva muri angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayihindura hydrolyzate kugira ngo ibumbe angiotensin ikuraho ubwonko (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ECA2 ishobora no gusenya izindi peptide zitandukanye, zirimo [des-Arg9]-bradiquinine, apaline, neurotensin, dinorphine A na ghrelin.
ECA2 kandi itegeka ingendo z'imyenda y'umushyitsi wa amino acid SLC6A19 nta cyo itwaye kandi yahuye n'indwara ya Hartnup.
