Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za software zigenewe ibikoresho bya telefoni zigenewe gufasha mu gukurikirana abahuye na coronavirus y'umwaka wa 2019-2020, ni ukuvuga uburyo bwo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wafashwe.
Hariho uburyo butandukanye bw'ikoranabuhanga bwakoreshejwe mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe no mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe, kandi Leta yabikomeje.
Ibikorwaremezo bitandukanye byateguwe ku bijyanye no gukora porogaramu zo gukurikirana abagenzi.
Hari ibibazo by'umutekano by'abantu, cyane cyane ku birebana na sisitemu zishingiye ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Hari indi nzira zidahuta cyane, urugero nko gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu abone uko yegereye telefoni z'abandi.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Apple na Google batangaje mu bufatanye ko bazashyiraho uburyo bwo gushyigikira izi porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu zabo za iOS na Android.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, hamwe na Alipay, bashyizeho porogaramu yemerera abaturage kureba niba bahuye n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Ubu ikoreshwa mu mijyi irenga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore ikoreshwa porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Iyo porogaramu yashinzwe n'umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga wo muri ako karere, yashyizwe ahagaragara nk'ikigo gisanzwe cy'ibanze, kandi izashyikirizwa leta. Muri Macedonia ya Ruguru hashyizweho porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth "StopKorona!", igamije gukurikirana ibyago by'abantu bashobora kwandura no guhita itanga igisubizo ku nzego z'ubuzima.
