U Bushinwa bufite gahunda yo gushyiraho uburyo bwo gupima abantu mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga (geoperimetry) ku barwayi baba i Moscou kandi bamaze gushyirwaho indwara ya COVID-19, hagamijwe ko batava mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha ubwenegihugu mu bijyanye n'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yagaragaje ibibazo bitandukanye by'ikoranabuhanga ku buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga bibaho mu gihe hashyizweho porogaramu zishingiye ku mbuga nkoranyambaga, harimo ko ari nziza kandi ko bishobora kuba bidafite akamaro mu gihe gusa igice gito cy'abaturage kizajya cyakira porogaramu.
