Muri Mata 2020, hari igikorwa cyo gusuzuma imikorere y'ubuvuzi ku rukingo n'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa mu kurwanya COVID-19. Hari imiti itandukanye ya virusi igenewe kuvura COVID-19, harimo: remdesivir, chlorokine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferone-beta.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hari ibimenyetso by'uko Remdesivir ifite akamaro.
Abaganga bavurwa bakoresheje remdesivir mu buryo buteye impuhwe bagaragaye ko bagaragaje ko bafite ubuhanga mu kwivuza.
Icyiciro cya III cy'igeragezwa ry'ubuvuzi kirimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Chloroquine, yahoze ikoreshwa mu kuvura malariya, yagenzuye mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020.
Icyakora, hari ibisabwa kugira ngo ubushakashatsi bugende neza.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya n'u Bushinwa batanga inama ku bijyanye no gukoresha kloroquine.
