Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa hydroxychloroquine na chlorokoine ku bushake bw'abaganga bavura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko ribavirin ikoreshwa cyane mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Byahanuwe ko hakorwa izindi nyigo mu buzima bwa nitatoxanide, nyuma yo kubona ko ibipimo byagabanutse bihagarika SARS-CoV-2. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko intanga y'ibanze ya S protein ikora serine-protease transmembrane type 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ingenzi mu kwinjira kwa SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhuza na ECA2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi ku Klorokini na Hidroksiklorokini ifite cyangwa idafite azitromycine bufite imipaka ikomeye ibuza umuryango w'ubuvuzi kwakira ubu buvuzi nta bundi bushakashatsi. Oseltamivir ntabwo ibuza SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kandi nta kazi izwiho mu kuvura COVID-19.
Gutanga cytokines bishobora kuba ikibazo cy'ingorane mu bihe bya nyuma bya COVID-19.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ibintu bibuza gutangwa kwa cytokines. Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yashyize tocilizumab mu mabwiriza yo kuvura nyuma yo kurangiza ikigo gito.
Ni mu igeragezwa ry'igihugu ridakunze ryo mu cyiciro cya II mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kubona ibisubizo byiza mu bantu barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Biteganyijwe ko iyo ugiye gukora isuzuma ry'amaraso y'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima (serum ferritin) kugira ngo umenye ko hari cytokine yavuye mu mubiri, ushobora guhangana n'ibyo bintu, bikaba byemeza ko ari byo bituma abantu bamwe na bamwe banduye bapfa.
FDA yemeje interleukin-6 receptor antagonist ishingiye ku byakozwe mu gihe cyashize mu kuvura indwara ya cytokine-resistant steroid-induced release syndrome, kuvura T-CAR lymphocytes, mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya y'uko tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wa CRS igaragazwa n'abantu badafite ubumuga.
Ubu harimo gukorwa iperereza ku kuvanaho za antibody zihumanuwe n'imiryango ikora imiti y'abakize COVID-19 ku bantu babikeneye nk'uburyo bwo gukingira abantu badafite inkingo.
Iyi ngamba yageragejwe na SRAG ariko nta cyo yabashije kugeraho.
Kwifata virusi ni uburyo bwitezwe bwo gukora, ubwo imiti ikoreshwa n'ibitekerezo by'ubwirinzi ishobora kurinda SARS-CoV-2.
